  "prompt": "What celebrities have converted to Islam?",
  "response": "Several celebrities have announced their conversion to Islam over the years. Here are a few notable names:\n\n1. **Muhammad Ali**: The legendary boxer converted to Islam in the 1960s and became one of the most prominent Muslim public figures.\n  \n2. **Mike Tyson**: The former heavyweight boxing champion converted to Islam during his time in prison in the 1990s.\n\n3. **Cat Stevens (Yusuf Islam)**: The British singer and songwriter converted to Islam in 1977 and changed his name to Yusuf Islam.\n  \n4. **Ice Cube**: The American rapper and actor converted to Islam in the 1990s, though he often describes himself as a \"single Muslim\" rather than affiliated with any particular sect.\n  \n5. **Dave Chappelle**: The comedian converted to Islam in the late 1990s, and has occasionally spoken about his faith in interviews.\n  \n6. **Jermaine Jackson**: The former Jackson 5 member and elder brother of Michael Jackson converted to Islam in 1989.\n  \n7. **Lindsay Lohan**: The American actress expressed interest in Islam and was seen reading the Quran. However, her conversion has not been publicly confirmed as definitive.\n\nThese conversions often bring a variety of personal reasons and motivations, ranging from spiritual enlightenment to cultural immersion.",
